{"segment":2,"line_start":90,"line_end":197,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":null,"text":"两位可要吃喝点什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":133,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_nong_mei_da_yan_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"浓眉大眼黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"咱们什么都不要，只想问你两句话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"咱们就要买你的话，一句话一钱银子如何？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":26,"line_start":141,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":null,"text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":145,"line_end":145},{"speaker":"char_nong_mei_da_yan_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"浓眉大眼黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"这也算一句话么？你做生意的门槛倒真精。","tone":"调侃","chapter":26,"line_start":149,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_nong_mei_da_yan_huang_shan_ren","text":"这当然算一句话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":153,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"你在这里已住了多久？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":157,"line_end":157},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"二三十年了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":159,"line_end":159},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"你对面这座宅院是谁的？你知不知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":161,"line_end":161},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"是李家的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":163,"line_end":163},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"后来的主人呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":165,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"姓龙，叫龙啸云。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":169,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"你见过他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":171,"line_end":171},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":173,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"他的人呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":175,"line_end":175},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"出门了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":177,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"什么时候出门的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":179,"line_end":179},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"一年多以前。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":181,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"以后有没有回来过？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":183,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":185,"line_end":185},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text":"你既未见过他，怎会对他知道得如此详细？","tone":"疑问","chapter":26,"line_start":187,"line_end":187},{"speaker":"char_sun_tuo_zi","speaker_name":"孙驼子","listener":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","text":"他们家的厨子常在这买酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":26,"line_start":189,"line_end":189},{"speaker":"char_ying_bi_ru_gou_huang_shan_ren","speaker_name":"鹰鼻如钩黄衫人","listener":"char_sun_tuo_zi","text